Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know why we'd received our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:28.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Why we all had come into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:34.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know how to face the one beside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only I looked away and wandered where to love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Though it was always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}If I have a tough, iron armor protecting the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I wonder if I can see you, and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}I just want to be stronger than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:57.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}To hold you, all of, oh even the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}All the dreams end up as mere dreams, even if game's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I won't give up my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even a hope may be said 'Just that's a thought'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}So I still want to reach for you hoping you live your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only there's a truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:16.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Living for making all the moments shine with proving all times
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Just seeing your smiles, that's my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even if we're all even in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:28.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我們是為何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:34.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}愛一直就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我卻總是視若不見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}彷徨著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}如有足以保護世界的強大鋼鐵鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}是否能一直見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}迸發無人能及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:57.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}去保護你的心靈 你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:02.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}如果夢想只能作為夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使窮途末路 我也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}抓住零光片羽的希望光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:09.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}讓你一直能做真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:16.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我們現在和過去的一切在此綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}你的笑靨 我的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:22.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使在暗無天日的世界裡
Comment: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================AVANT=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,直升機停機坪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,客人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,實在招待不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是他吧 他來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要殺了我逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為不想傷害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著 G2 放開她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,開槍打我然後逃走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它什麼都不會做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有所覺悟 你應該能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來你只有這種程度的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我就開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜歡弄髒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是你輸了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雷納德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放開那把槍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,卡力林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,傷口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎只是擦傷 真亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那也是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,被看破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,韋伯 你還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 你能逃到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,通信干擾 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,電子戰也是對面佔優
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有新的客人 馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人似乎也出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 撿了一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 我比較擔心宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 新的敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？ 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然目標女人逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但要問你的事情像山一樣多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,綁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我想起了溪山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 雷蒙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,作戰失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,相良宗介 現在投下烈焰魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰… 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是它自稱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這個機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.42,AI,,0,0,0,,好久不見 軍曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.26,AI,,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:33.85,AI,,0,0,0,,但本機的名稱是ARX-8 烈焰魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.82,AI,,0,0,0,,相良軍曹 請允許我回歸你的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然 我允許
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.63,AI,,0,0,0,,很光榮 首先請搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:55.15,AI,,0,0,0,,警告 敵AS巨獸3台 地獄君王3台接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.64,AI,,0,0,0,,要先大鬧一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:05.04,AI,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這個力量是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.05,AI,,0,0,0,,失禮了 這台機體沒有試運行過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.34,AI,,0,0,0,,λ-Driver嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.66,AI,,0,0,0,,不知道 因為沒用過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢 試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.00,AI,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.00,AI,,0,0,0,,成功 看來能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.26,AI,,0,0,0,,接近警報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.08,AI,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.22,AI,,0,0,0,,保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,輔助臂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.86,AI,,0,0,0,,由我來控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.63,AI,,0,0,0,,現在的負荷推定1500噸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.25,AI,,0,0,0,,請馬上逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有其他武器了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.92,AI,,0,0,0,,請用這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,165mm？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.35,AI,,0,0,0,,威力和後座力都很驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.67,AI,,0,0,0,,沒有λ-Driver無法開炮 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,強制擊發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.49,AI,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:36.91,AI,,0,0,0,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.74,AI,,0,0,0,,貫穿對方的力場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.94,AI,,0,0,0,,一台巨獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.09,AI,,0,0,0,,放棄戰鬥撤退中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.73,AI,,0,0,0,,要追擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以這個武器的射程已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.93,AI,,0,0,0,,不 是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:11.43,AI,,0,0,0,,爆破炮 切換至榴彈模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.20,AI,,0,0,0,,最大射程是30km
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.92,AI,,0,0,0,,命中 擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,脫離危險空域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好 保持這個高度 向北北西去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的 現在馬上掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你還蠻精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,掉頭回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我會射這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你便 畢竟是自己的槍都管理不好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:12:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真開槍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛才對雷納德・泰斯特羅莎做的那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有開槍覺悟的人不能拿槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,強迫自己的意志就意味著傷害什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到 所以現在在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 我已經沒法見到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定 把槍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 我會盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,讓直升機回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那個還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,需要為雷納德治傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,還有被敵人擊墜的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把槍放下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那讓我道別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,無線通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可是這全是宗介幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好可靠的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是當時這傢伙在美麗達島上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,待會兒再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我盡量不想讓俘虜看到那個機體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\b0\bord0\be2\c&H535651&\frz327.1\pos(935.667,492.333)}妖精的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fsp2\pos(915,995)}Electromagnetic Camouflage System
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,AL 發動ECS 不可視模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.76,AI,,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:13.21,AI,,0,0,0,,這台機體沒有搭載ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.77,AI,,0,0,0,,犯規的力量 λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:20.69,AI,,0,0,0,,沒有空間搭載多餘的電子器材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒有電子裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是現代戰爭 你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.15,AI,,0,0,0,,可以和同伴進行數據連接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.00,AI,,0,0,0,,不要灰心加油吧 軍曹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有個多餘的器材哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,應該把你扔進垃圾桶 換成ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.54,AI,,0,0,0,,這個提議是荒謬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.57,AI,,0,0,0,,沒有我 這個機體是派不上用場的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.06,AI,,0,0,0,,捕捉到新的無線信號 似乎在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.56,AI,,0,0,0,,要接上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥 是千鳥嗎 你在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,來這裡之前發生了很多 我猶豫了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了 為了救出你 帶你回那個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,住手？ 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我想尋求自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有人會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 恭子也是 發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經無法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 忘掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讓它結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就到此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事絕對不要 就算有人受傷也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動 讓我說到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 我命令你 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,無論付出什麼犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,無論死多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,死幾百 幾萬 幾億人都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以來接我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把那沒有常識 給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,亂七八糟的軍人技能全用上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多麼難纏的對手都打個落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吧 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會去的 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 下次見面以後 一定要接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,盡情的 無論在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 幾億人只是打比方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被你擺了一道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你真打算尋死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是演的 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 我有所覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你去死吧 下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,時隔半年一見面就來這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 你不是成長了很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,總之沒事就好 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有話過後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,無線通訊我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,介紹你的長官給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然一口氣就過來了 但先要交涉才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,長官 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,照顧我 照顧我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙無視掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我才需要照顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,照顧 照顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 我來介紹他
